public enum InGameWesternCharacter extends Enum<InGameWesternCharacter>
An enumeration whose purpose is to convert the characters used in Western PokÃ©mon games into characters that can be used in Java strings. value -> the numeric value corresponding to the character in the in-game encoding character -> the character in its "regular" version.
